1
00:00:35,159 --> 00:00:35,799
Stay concealed

2
00:00:36,720 --> 00:00:37,520
Watch the firing position

3
00:00:44,360 --> 00:00:44,919
Captain Duan

4
00:00:45,159 --> 00:00:47,240
There's something I don't know if I should say

5
00:00:47,479 --> 00:00:48,159
Say it

6
00:00:48,240 --> 00:00:49,319
Poachers

7
00:00:49,319 --> 00:00:51,319
usually use homemade hunting guns

8
00:00:51,479 --> 00:00:53,520
That shot just now probably hit prey

9
00:00:53,880 --> 00:00:54,840
But this kind of gun

10
00:00:54,840 --> 00:00:55,959
is just really loud

11
00:00:56,240 --> 00:00:57,520
And the echo in the mountains is strong

12
00:00:57,799 --> 00:00:58,959
It's hard to tell the direction

13
00:01:00,240 --> 00:01:01,560
What exactly are you trying to say

14
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:03,919
Based on my

15
00:01:03,919 --> 00:01:06,120
years of experience in the woods

16
00:01:06,559 --> 00:01:08,360
the place that shot came from

17
00:01:08,559 --> 00:01:09,400
is from us

18
00:01:09,959 --> 00:01:11,080
at least two kilometers away

19
00:01:15,360 --> 00:01:16,800
Then what are you acting up for here

20
00:01:19,720 --> 00:01:21,599
I just got carried away, okay

21
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:24,800
When poachers go into the mountains

22
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:26,120
it's at least three to five days each time

23
00:01:26,879 --> 00:01:28,599
Don't just tough it out here

24
00:01:28,599 --> 00:01:29,319
Come with me

25
00:01:29,839 --> 00:01:31,760
Why would I go with you

26
00:01:31,919 --> 00:01:32,879
The woods are so huge

27
00:01:32,879 --> 00:01:33,639
Which way do we go

28
00:01:35,239 --> 00:01:37,080
Would you believe me if I said I dreamed it

29
00:01:38,080 --> 00:01:38,480
I...

30
00:01:41,800 --> 00:01:42,680
She's not in a good state of mind

31
00:01:44,080 --> 00:01:45,440
I'm not as good as you at solving cases

32
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,400
But in the woods, you're no match for me

33
00:01:48,199 --> 00:01:49,000
Don't listen to her nonsense

34
00:01:49,279 --> 00:01:49,760
Enough

35
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:50,599
Stop talking

36
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:52,120
How about this

37
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:52,760
Xiao Lu is right

38
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:56,080
Just waiting here isn't a solution

39
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:57,279
Shitou

40
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:58,760
You stay here and watch the car

41
00:01:59,239 --> 00:02:00,160
Lu Yi and I will go into the mountains

42
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:01,160
That's an order

43
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:01,800
Yes

44
00:02:02,360 --> 00:02:02,800
Move

45
00:02:03,519 --> 00:02:04,080
Well

46
00:03:26,839 --> 00:03:27,919
Police! Don't move

47
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:33,160
Killing a chicken

48
00:03:33,399 --> 00:03:34,320
or shooting a bird

49
00:03:35,479 --> 00:03:36,919
doesn't call for this big a show, does it

50
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:39,919
I doubt all you shot was a bird

51
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:41,520
You were caught red-handed

52
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:42,759
What else is there to say

53
00:03:43,279 --> 00:03:44,360
Oh, give me a break

54
00:03:44,880 --> 00:03:45,960
I've already checked

55
00:03:46,199 --> 00:03:47,039
That thing of mine

56
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:48,279
its power

57
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:49,600
is really, really low

58
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:52,119
it doesn't count as making an illegal gun

59
00:03:52,119 --> 00:03:53,520
Quit dodging the important part

60
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,000
Now talk

61
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,839
What's the deal with the body parts at Dahong Restaurant

62
00:03:59,679 --> 00:04:00,360
What are you talking about

63
00:04:00,679 --> 00:04:03,000
What's the deal with the body parts at Dahong Restaurant

64
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:05,119
Body parts

65
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:08,000
No

66
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:13,360
Anyone here

67
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,079
Anyone here

68
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,079
Hello

69
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:24,279
We're from the Criminal Investigation Detachment

70
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,440
We need to ask you about some things

71
00:04:30,359 --> 00:04:31,040
Everyone, don't be nervous

72
00:04:31,679 --> 00:04:33,519
Just tell us whatever you know

73
00:04:34,799 --> 00:04:36,160
We're not nervous, not nervous

74
00:04:38,839 --> 00:04:41,000
Any personnel changes at the lumber camp lately

75
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:41,720
Anyone gone missing

76
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:43,679
No

77
00:04:44,519 --> 00:04:45,119
No

78
00:04:46,559 --> 00:04:47,079
Are you sure

79
00:04:47,679 --> 00:04:48,600
Think carefully

80
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:51,480
Really, no

81
00:04:56,239 --> 00:04:56,679
What are you doing

82
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:57,559
Let go of my hand

83
00:05:07,359 --> 00:05:08,200
Illegal group gambling

84
00:05:09,679 --> 00:05:11,079
Talk here or back at the station

85
00:05:11,839 --> 00:05:12,920
I'll confess

86
00:05:13,359 --> 00:05:13,880
This...

87
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,000
These are Yang Dazhi's gambling tools

88
00:05:16,279 --> 00:05:17,200
He has nothing to do with us

89
00:05:17,279 --> 00:05:18,160
Really, nothing to do with us

90
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:19,079
Where's Yang Dazhi

91
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:21,399
Yang Dazhi

92
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:23,239
hasn't come for a few days

93
00:05:24,239 --> 00:05:25,040
Liu Ping too

94
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:26,760
hasn't come

95
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:27,760
Where did he go

96
00:05:28,839 --> 00:05:29,440
Well...

97
00:05:30,239 --> 00:05:31,200
I really don't know

98
00:05:31,760 --> 00:05:32,679
Maybe

99
00:05:33,359 --> 00:05:34,640
he's off gambling somewhere

100
00:05:34,839 --> 00:05:35,519
won some money

101
00:05:35,839 --> 00:05:36,600
and quit

102
00:05:39,160 --> 00:05:39,959
Those toiletries

103
00:05:40,279 --> 00:05:41,640
which belong to Yang Dazhi and Liu Ping

104
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:43,640
This one

105
00:05:44,320 --> 00:05:45,239
This one is Yang Dazhi's

106
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,480
This one is Liu Ping's

107
00:05:51,519 --> 00:05:52,559
Where's your boss

108
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:54,279
Boss

109
00:05:55,239 --> 00:05:55,839
The boss

110
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,279
Qiao Sanbao

111
00:05:58,880 --> 00:06:01,000
He lives in the house in back

112
00:06:02,239 --> 00:06:03,359
But he may not be there

113
00:06:03,839 --> 00:06:04,640
But the boss's wife

114
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:05,640
should be there

115
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:06,519
Just...

116
00:06:06,519 --> 00:06:07,040
That room right there

117
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:08,320
That's the room

118
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,000
What happened to your face

119
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:36,959
I bumped into something by accident

120
00:06:43,559 --> 00:06:44,480
Your name is Liu Li

121
00:06:47,119 --> 00:06:49,600
and you are married to lumberyard boss Qiao Sanbao

122
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,279
Yes

123
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,519
Qiao Sanbao hasn't been around these past few days

124
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:56,720
Yes

125
00:06:57,279 --> 00:07:00,200
He said he went out to discuss business

126
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:01,799
Where did he go

127
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:03,119
He didn't tell you

128
00:07:05,079 --> 00:07:06,079
He doesn't let me ask

129
00:07:07,440 --> 00:07:08,480
I can't control him either

130
00:07:15,959 --> 00:07:18,359
The lumberyard workers Yang Dazhi and Liu Ping

131
00:07:18,799 --> 00:07:20,200
also haven't come to work these past few days

132
00:07:20,760 --> 00:07:21,480
Did they ask for leave

133
00:07:23,679 --> 00:07:24,399
No

134
00:07:25,079 --> 00:07:26,519
You and Liu Ping are sister and brother

135
00:07:27,559 --> 00:07:28,880
I can't control anyone

136
00:07:30,239 --> 00:07:31,040
What I'm asking is

137
00:07:31,239 --> 00:07:33,640
are you and Liu Ping sister and brother

138
00:07:36,559 --> 00:07:37,399
Yes

139
00:07:40,519 --> 00:07:42,359
I heard Yang Dazhi and Liu Ping had a conflict

140
00:07:43,079 --> 00:07:43,679
Is that right

141
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:45,079
No

142
00:07:47,079 --> 00:07:48,160
I don't know either

143
00:07:53,959 --> 00:07:56,399
Based on the DNA extracted from the forest dorm

144
00:07:56,399 --> 00:07:57,519
after comparison

145
00:07:57,760 --> 00:07:59,000
it can now be confirmed

146
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,799
the deceased was a logging camp worker

147
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:01,720
Yang Dazhi

148
00:08:06,079 --> 00:08:07,000
Let's hear it

149
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:07,799
What do you think?

150
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,440
I think

151
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:12,799
logger Liu Ping

152
00:08:12,799 --> 00:08:13,920
is highly suspicious

153
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:16,799
According to the other workers at the logging camp

154
00:08:17,519 --> 00:08:19,000
Liu Ping and Yang Dazhi

155
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:20,399
went missing on the same day

156
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,239
Yang Dazhi was a compulsive gambler

157
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,720
and had borrowed money from Liu Ping

158
00:08:24,799 --> 00:08:26,160
The two of them, over the repayment issue

159
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,000
even got into a conflict

160
00:08:27,839 --> 00:08:28,559
Also

161
00:08:28,839 --> 00:08:30,480
a chainsaw just went missing from the logging camp

162
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:33,799
Qiao Sanbao is also a suspect

163
00:08:34,119 --> 00:08:35,359
His whereabouts are currently unknown

164
00:08:35,760 --> 00:08:37,080
I learned indirectly

165
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:38,359
that this Yang Dazhi

166
00:08:38,359 --> 00:08:40,239
often took advantage of Qiao Sanbao being away

167
00:08:40,760 --> 00:08:41,440
and, using drunkenness as an excuse

168
00:08:41,520 --> 00:08:43,239
harassed Qiao Sanbao's wife, Liu Li

169
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:44,640
So we can't rule out

170
00:08:44,799 --> 00:08:46,559
the possibility that Qiao Sanbao killed in revenge

171
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,599
I think Lin Shen is right

172
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:49,880
The poacher also confessed

173
00:08:49,880 --> 00:08:50,479
that a lot of wild game

174
00:08:50,479 --> 00:08:52,039
he got from Qiao Sanbao

175
00:08:52,479 --> 00:08:53,799
then resold to Dahong Restaurant

176
00:08:54,479 --> 00:08:55,159
In other words

177
00:08:55,159 --> 00:08:57,640
both had motive and opportunity

178
00:08:59,559 --> 00:09:01,960
Of course, joint involvement can't be ruled out

179
00:09:07,239 --> 00:09:08,039
Lu Yi

180
00:09:11,760 --> 00:09:12,919
That poacher also said

181
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:14,760
that in the back of the freezer truck

182
00:09:14,799 --> 00:09:16,559
there was still lots of unsold game meat

183
00:09:26,400 --> 00:09:26,960
The severed finger

184
00:09:27,640 --> 00:09:28,520
belongs to Liu Ping

185
00:09:32,039 --> 00:09:33,479
Looks like we need to question Liu Li again

186
00:09:34,919 --> 00:09:36,119
I jumped to conclusions

187
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:38,400
thinking the finger and body parts were from one person

188
00:09:38,679 --> 00:09:40,239
But the DNA test results show

189
00:09:40,479 --> 00:09:41,440
this finger

190
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:42,960
belongs to Liu Ping

191
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,280
In that case

192
00:09:46,359 --> 00:09:48,559
Liu Ping has most likely already been killed

193
00:09:50,520 --> 00:09:52,320
Then Qiao Sanbao is under major suspicion

194
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:53,359
Haozi

195
00:09:53,479 --> 00:09:53,880
Here

196
00:09:54,320 --> 00:09:55,359
You and Lin Shen

197
00:09:55,679 --> 00:09:56,719
keep a close watch on the forest camp

198
00:09:57,359 --> 00:09:57,880
Yes

199
00:10:03,479 --> 00:10:04,159
Um

200
00:10:04,679 --> 00:10:06,520
we may need to trouble you again

201
00:10:08,159 --> 00:10:08,760
It's work

202
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:09,599
That's only right

203
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:10,520
It's just that

204
00:10:10,760 --> 00:10:11,679
this workload

205
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:13,640
maybe this job

206
00:10:13,880 --> 00:10:16,200
just has a bit too much work

207
00:10:31,239 --> 00:10:31,840
Give it to me

208
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:34,960
And this too

209
00:10:36,479 --> 00:10:37,119
Thanks for your hard work

210
00:10:38,359 --> 00:10:38,880
Captain Duan

211
00:10:39,520 --> 00:10:40,200
This is the last box

212
00:10:40,919 --> 00:10:41,599
If

213
00:10:41,599 --> 00:10:43,039
what the poacher said is true

214
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:44,280
then in here

215
00:10:44,760 --> 00:10:46,039
there should be Liu Ping's body parts

216
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:48,679
Did you think of that just now?

217
00:10:49,559 --> 00:10:50,960
I just felt

218
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:53,719
there might be more than one victim

219
00:10:54,119 --> 00:10:55,280
But honestly

220
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:57,039
I didn't expect it to be Liu Ping

221
00:10:58,280 --> 00:10:59,080
To be a detective

222
00:10:59,280 --> 00:11:00,679
you need that kind of instinct

223
00:11:00,679 --> 00:11:01,359
Very good

224
00:11:02,239 --> 00:11:02,760
Captain Duan

225
00:11:03,479 --> 00:11:05,520
If I join your team in the future

226
00:11:05,679 --> 00:11:06,479
would you welcome me?

227
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:11,440
Let's talk about that later

228
00:11:11,640 --> 00:11:12,359
We'll see how you perform

229
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:14,239
Come with me to the forensics room

230
00:11:14,559 --> 00:11:15,239
Yes

231
00:11:20,799 --> 00:11:22,799
We found Liu Ping's severed finger among the remains

232
00:11:24,599 --> 00:11:26,200
Your younger brother may already have been killed

233
00:11:31,239 --> 00:11:32,479
Your husband, Qiao Sanbao

234
00:11:32,760 --> 00:11:33,640
where exactly did he go?

235
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:44,359
We now suspect

236
00:11:44,359 --> 00:11:45,760
Yang Dazhi's death and your brother's disappearance

237
00:11:45,760 --> 00:11:46,840
are both connected to Qiao Sanbao

238
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:48,359
You'd better tell us everything you know

239
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:53,400
I don't know

240
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:56,080
You've already asked many times

241
00:11:57,239 --> 00:11:58,280
I really don't know

242
00:12:03,520 --> 00:12:04,559
What's going on?

243
00:12:05,159 --> 00:12:06,239
You two worked at this for so long

244
00:12:06,919 --> 00:12:08,440
What, are you living off nothing?

245
00:12:08,799 --> 00:12:10,080
Aren't you ashamed?

246
00:12:10,400 --> 00:12:11,159
From now on, don't say

247
00:12:11,159 --> 00:12:12,119
you're from our Second Squad

248
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:13,280
Don't say I trained you

249
00:12:15,359 --> 00:12:16,200
What is it, Captain?

250
00:12:17,679 --> 00:12:18,960
These two idiots

251
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:20,159
worked forever

252
00:12:20,159 --> 00:12:21,239
and got nothing out of her

253
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:28,440
Captain Duan

254
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:30,919
I'm a woman

255
00:12:31,280 --> 00:12:32,520
Why don't you let me try?

256
00:12:39,799 --> 00:12:40,679
Lin Shen and I together

257
00:12:43,280 --> 00:12:44,080
That works

258
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:51,679
After DNA comparison

259
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:54,679
the body parts are neither Liu Ping's

260
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:56,239
nor are they

261
00:12:57,400 --> 00:12:58,239
Yang Dazhi's

262
00:12:59,119 --> 00:12:59,919
but rather

263
00:13:02,119 --> 00:13:03,440
Qiao Sanbao

264
00:13:16,760 --> 00:13:17,359
Brother San

265
00:13:17,880 --> 00:13:18,760
Today's goods

266
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,039
are quite big

267
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:23,479
This is the last time today

268
00:13:23,479 --> 00:13:24,159
I'm not selling anymore

269
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:25,960
Don't come again

270
00:13:26,280 --> 00:13:28,080
Why quit such good business?

271
00:13:30,679 --> 00:13:31,239
Brother San

272
00:13:32,039 --> 00:13:33,359
You turning against money now?

273
00:13:36,320 --> 00:13:37,919
Brother San, what happened to your hand?

274
00:13:39,640 --> 00:13:40,520
It's nothing

275
00:13:40,799 --> 00:13:42,200
While cleaning up this stuff

276
00:13:42,559 --> 00:13:43,359
I did it by accident

277
00:13:45,039 --> 00:13:45,440
All right then

278
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:46,679
Then I'll head back first

279
00:13:50,599 --> 00:13:51,239
Go
